      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>Wait, really? 911?? That sounds super intense. I mean, I've had the shakes before when I'm just stressed or something. Are you sure it's that serious? I feel okay otherwise, just a bit queasy. Can't I just drink a ton of water and see if that helps flush it out or something?",
